This software includes a pure Common Lisp implementation of:
- SHA-256 cryptographic hash function (FIPS 180-4)
- Merkle tree construction (Bitcoin-compatible)
- SPV proof generation and verification

Originally extracted from the CLPIC (Common Lisp P2P Intellectual Property Chain)
project for standalone use.

The SHA-256 implementation follows NIST FIPS 180-4:
https://csrc.nist.gov/publications/detail/fips/180/4/final

The Merkle tree implementation is compatible with Bitcoin's merkle tree format
as specified in the Bitcoin protocol documentation.
